{"id":232345411,"title":"#問 閱讀筆記本","content":"大家好\n\n一直想找本閱讀筆記本來記錄自己的閱讀心得、佳句\n\n最近從圖書館借了一堆書結果都堆在桌上 毫無進度😂\n加上每天都被老師追進度\n所以下定決心要來找本筆記本記錄閱讀心得順便督促自己 \n\n剛開始是看到他們家出了一系列的主題筆記本\n（超想買旅館！！）\n但不知道紙質還有寫起來的感覺如何\n（主要應該用sarasa寫 不會用鋼筆）\n之前有買過台灣出的主題筆記本 結果紙很厚寫起來感覺很像圖畫紙（？）\n看這本的格式比較大 旁邊還可以貼照片\n\n\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/DzLdtDr.png\n\n剛才看到這本\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/WPHjVVo.png\n總共可以寫40本\n感覺每本的空間比較剛好\n\n想請問有沒有人用過或者有其他的閱讀筆記本選項\n目前傾向迪夢奇的 比較容易購入\n其實也是可以直接從櫃子裡拿一本筆記本出來寫\n但是\n人生還是要有一點樂趣 😂\n\n\n感謝大家","excerpt":"大家好，一直想找本閱讀筆記本來記錄自己的閱讀心得、佳句，最近從圖書館借了一堆書結果都堆在桌上 毫無進度，加上每天都被老師追進度，所以下定決心要來找本筆記本記錄閱讀心得順便督促自己，剛開始是看到他們家出","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f74a0662-cb27-4d45-a6b7-7f87d3d02396","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-10-21T14:42:11.158Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-21T14:44:48.600Z","commentCount":7,"likeCount":27,"tags":[],"topics":["筆記本"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"文具","forumAlias":"stationery","school":"東海大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":27}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/DzLdtDr.png"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/WPHjVVo.png"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"febe1629-6454-4b73-9d6b-7d10a930b39c","url":"https://i.imgur.com/DzLdtDrl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/DzLdtDrl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/DzLdtDrl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-21T14:42:11.158Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-21T14:44:48.600Z"},{"id":"febe1629-6454-4b73-9d6b-7d10a930b39c","url":"http://i.imgur.com/DzLdtDr.png","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/DzLdtDr","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/DzLdtDrl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-21T14:42:11.158Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-21T14:44